# 🧮 Modern Calculator

### 🔗 Live Demo
[modern-calculator-ap-t8na.bolt.host](https://modern-calculator-ap-t8na.bolt.host/)
[modern_calculator_base44](https://nova-calc-01339b1d.base44.app/)

### 📘 Overview
A simple yet powerful calculator application built with **Python** as the backend and a **responsive frontend**.  
Performs addition, subtraction, multiplication, division, and exponentiation.

### ⚙️ Tech Stack
- Python
-Prompt Engineering
-Bolt,Base44
- Hosting: Bolt Host, Base44 Host

### 💡 Features
- Clean UI for quick calculations  
- Handles division by zero and invalid input  
- Deployed online for public use  

